            <div class="paragraph col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-8 col-md-offset-2"><p>The UK generates 700,000 tonnes of furniture waste each year, with 70% going to landfill, the majority of which is still usable. Can furniture be designed to encourage less wasteful behaviour, yet still satisfy our desire for novelty and change?</p></div>
            <div class="clear col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-8 col-md-offset-2"><img class="project-image" src="units-problem.jpg"/></div>
